  <title>Entities</title>
  <body id="body">
    <p>An <term>entity</term><indexterm>entity</indexterm> is a reusable fragment of the document content that can be reused multiple times by reference.</p>
    <p>Unlike other editors, Serna allows you to edit entity references in-place and shows them as regular content.</p>
    <p>There are two types of entities:<ol>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="internal-entity.xml">Internal Entities</xref></p>
          <p conref="internal-entity.xml#internal-entity/internal-entity-intro"/>
        </li>
        <li>
          <p><xref href="external-entity.xml">External Entities</xref></p>
          <p conref="external-entity.xml#external-entity/external-entity-intro"/>
        </li>
      </ol></p>
